{"tid":1914390,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗緊疫仲有冇得抗爭】和你做文青！","createTime":"2020-03-07T13:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T03:30:39.000Z","uid":350138,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"083ae6114637837fba673a5b6f084b3316038f2f","tid":1914390,"uid":350138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"(English translation below)<br />\n區選之後 成場運動好似慢慢到樽頸位<br />\n加埋個武肺又少左活動<br />\n不如就趁呢個時候<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">做下文青 睇下書增值自己 計劃下之後要點做</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n話說有日有個曾經參與幾場香港抗爭嘅美國佬睇左本由美國學者Gene Sharp寫嘅<br />\nSelf-Liberation: A Guide to Strategic Planning to End a Dictatorship or Other Oppression<br />\n大概講點樣<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">喺獨裁政權下解放</span></strong></span> #香港獨立唯一出路<br />\n包括：了解獨裁政權特點同弱點、點plan行動、要考慮咩問題、成功之後要點做等<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">啊美國佬覺得可能啱香港人用 但原著成二百幾頁好似長左少少<br />\n佢就抽左裡面最精華同有用嘅部分出黎 叫埋我一齊整左個簡短版 希望幫到香港抗爭者</span><br />\n<br />\n我地整嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\">簡短版</span> : <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/9e23xd942tdnjfz/Hong%20Kong%20Protest%20Edition.pdf?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2F9e23xd942tdnjfz%2FHong%2520Kong%2520Protest%2520Edition.pdf%3Fdl%3D0&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=eaa508dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/9e23xd942tdnjfz/Hong%20Kong%20Protest%20Edition.pdf?dl=0</a><br />\n想睇詳細啲 <span style=\"color: orange;\">原著</span>: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/3r1xcmhbm1bzags/hkdemocr.pdf?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2F3r1xcmhbm1bzags%2Fhkdemocr.pdf%3Fdl%3D0&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=3dbc0cf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/3r1xcmhbm1bzags/hkdemocr.pdf?dl=0</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個時間除左休養生息之外 真心都plan下之後可以點做<br />\n當然書裡面部分方法我地都試過 但<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">二百萬個精叻腦袋</span></strong>總有可能會諗到新野<br />\n美國佬同我希望提醒多次大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">革命尚未成功，同志仍須努力</span></span><br />\n睇完inspire到你嘅 動動腦轉轉彎 每個人都可以係organizer<br />\n<br />\n整graphic叻嘅手足 歡迎你拎書入面覺得有用嘅point整文宣<br />\n記得<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">SHARE</span></span></strong>俾各方好友 一齊默默看細細想 腦裡會轉出新方向<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n雖然縮短完都有成六十二頁 但由於佢係billingual 其實一半就睇哂~<br />\n<br />\n1. 獨立編著聲明Statement of Independent Creation +序Preface<br />\n2.《再生文化》Regenerative Culture<br />\n3.《四種改變的機制》 Four mechanisms of change（簡略原著中定義）<br />\n4. 所有註腳（新加入 我地自己interpret希望易啲理解）<br />\n<br />\n除左呢幾part係美國佬作同我翻譯之外 其他章節同翻譯都係出自原著<br />\n<br />\n利申 我地都都唔是專業作家同翻譯 有咩怪怪的就so99ly了<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"67c4b2bccedecc25a6d4b15133f104a906b27f06","tid":1914390,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:20:25.000Z","msg":"借位 大家幫手推一推<br />\n［行動post入黎推一推］ 明天1930將軍澳*準時到*<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1914250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1914250</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a3acfac54306727f344ae005dd55d1c31d5cf49f","tid":1914390,"uid":350138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:23:09.000Z","msg":"【Can we keep resisting while fighting Coronavirus?】Be educated with you!<br />\n<br />\nThe whole movement has gradually slowed down since the District Council Elections.<br />\nAnd the Wuhan Coronavirus has prevented us from protesting as much as we have been.<br />\nSo why don&rsquo;t we make good use of this time, be prepared for when we resume the struggle; <span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>Read some books, improve ourselves and plan what to do next?</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nOne day, an American guy who participated in some of the HK protests read a book called Self-Liberation: A Guide to Strategic Planning to End a Dictatorship or Other Oppression by an American scholar Gene Sharp.<br />\nBriefly talking about how to <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>liberate a society from a dictatorship and transition it to a democracy</strong></span></span><br />\n#HongKongIndependenceTheonlywayout<br />\nThe book wrote about getting to know the characteristics &amp; weaknesses of a dictatorship regime, how to plan actions, what to consider, what to do after success, and more.<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">The American thought it could be useful for HKers, but 213 pages might be a bit too long for those who are working full time, studying full-time and protesting so much.<br />\nSo he picked out what he believed are the most essential and most relevant parts to the HK protestors, and asked me to work on a shortened version, in an effort to help HK protestors</span><br />\n<br />\nDownload link of our <span style=\"color: orange;\">shortened version</span>: <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/9e23xd942tdnjfz/Hong%20Kong%20Protest%20Edition.pdf?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2F9e23xd942tdnjfz%2FHong%2520Kong%2520Protest%2520Edition.pdf%3Fdl%3D0&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=eaa508dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/9e23xd942tdnjfz/Hong%20Kong%20Protest%20Edition.pdf?dl=0</a><br />\nWant to read the entire original text? Download link of the <span style=\"color: orange;\">original work</span>: <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/3r1xcmhbm1bzags/hkdemocr.pdf?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2F3r1xcmhbm1bzags%2Fhkdemocr.pdf%3Fdl%3D0&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=3dbc0cf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/3r1xcmhbm1bzags/hkdemocr.pdf?dl=0</a><br />\n<br />\nApart from taking good rest at this time, we should really start planning what to do next<br />\nOf course we&rsquo;ve tried part of the methods mentioned in the book, but <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">2 million smart brains</span> can always think of something new<br />\nThe American guy and I would like to remind all of you again<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&ldquo;Revolution has not succeeded yet, comrades still need to struggle.&rdquo;<br />\n</span></span>If the book can inspire you, think hard; everyone can be an organizer<br />\n<br />\nWhoever is good at graphics, we welcome you to take useful points from the book and make promo materials<br />\nPlease <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>SHARE</strong></span></span> with your friends; read and think together, it may mean a new and better direction moving forward.<br />\n<br />\nAlthough it&rsquo;s still 62 pages after our editing, because it&rsquo;s bilingual, you&rsquo;ll only have to read half the pages! Here&rsquo;s what&rsquo;s new in the edited version:<br />\n1. Statement of Independent Creation+ Preface<br />\n2. Regenerative Culture <br />\n3. Four mechanisms of change (simplified original definitions)<br />\n4. All footnotes (There were none before; we added them for better understanding with our own interpretations)<br />\n<br />\nExcept for these few parts that were written by the American guy and translated by me, all other sections are from the original work.<br />\n<br />\nDisclaimer:<br />\nNeither of us are professional writers &amp; translators.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Liberate Hong Kong, Revolution of our times. Five demands, not one less.</span>"},{"pid":"d023d638353aa923520dfb6cc0f3ad53cb254ee8","tid":1914390,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:10:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86a1ec36ceafe643c40f1e4957b5939010521315","tid":1914390,"uid":74076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3ff25960b3439ddb00ef3d10002c0bb1cebeae56","tid":1914390,"uid":309331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ea654915115a67a0176eaadf80f2a44f96a2369b","tid":1914390,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:31:34.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"eb69b99ce92f0b07c10e6b0d821c34c81a7f27be","tid":1914390,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"留名待睇"},{"pid":"e30ab9b1ee20d831846fbfe9789cd0290ff446ed","tid":1914390,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c3d4f0d6cafa7308ebc006c731ce253c6622ab","tid":1914390,"uid":77692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"吉恩&middot;夏普（Gene Sharp， 1928年1月21日－2018年1月28日）是一位哲學、政治學和社會學學者，以對權力和非暴力運動的著述著名，廣泛流傳於世界各地的社運界別，被視為全球茉莉花革命的「理論推手」，在西方國家享有「非暴力抵抗的教父」和「非暴力戰爭的克勞塞維茨」之名[3]，又有「<span style=\"color: red;\">非暴力抗爭</span>理論大師」之譽[4]。<br />\n小心被人話係左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdad0e41ca09c606bd0f327cfe111925953deb7b","tid":1914390,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c3d4f0d6cafa7308ebc006c731ce253c6622ab","tid":1914390,"uid":77692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"吉恩&middot;夏普（Gene Sharp， 1928年1月21日－2018年1月28日）是一位哲學、政治學和社會學學者，以對權力和非暴力運動的著述著名，廣泛流傳於世界各地的社運界別，被視為全球茉莉花革命的「理論推手」，在西方國家享有「非暴力抵抗的教父」和「非暴力戰爭的克勞塞維茨」之名[3]，又有「<span style=\"color: red;\">非暴力抗爭</span>理論大師」之譽[4]。<br />\n小心被人話係左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb5d2d42206c5b108afb08878b947f72cfe5505","tid":1914390,"uid":350138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"71c3d4f0d6cafa7308ebc006c731ce253c6622ab","tid":1914390,"uid":77692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"吉恩&middot;夏普（Gene Sharp， 1928年1月21日－2018年1月28日）是一位哲學、政治學和社會學學者，以對權力和非暴力運動的著述著名，廣泛流傳於世界各地的社運界別，被視為全球茉莉花革命的「理論推手」，在西方國家享有「非暴力抵抗的教父」和「非暴力戰爭的克勞塞維茨」之名[3]，又有「<span style=\"color: red;\">非暴力抗爭</span>理論大師」之譽[4]。<br />\n小心被人話係左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:49:49.000Z","msg":"我地都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺序戴左個頭盔<br />\n//我們堅信「兄弟爬山」此座右銘，但亦相信抗爭者可以更有效地運用個人力量，在街頭衝突以外轉戰其他非暴力政治反抗，如抵制和罷工。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">這絕非出於我們不認同目前抗爭者所為</span></strong>，而是事實上，政府於武力運用上不幸地永遠遠超抗爭者。//<br />\n<br />\n前線巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c10d9e5e7816c9a5f72c05974cb1a9e58561951","tid":1914390,"uid":350138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb69b99ce92f0b07c10e6b0d821c34c81a7f27be","tid":1914390,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"留名待睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:51:32.000Z","msg":"呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0bd00843a6c470a841eef608630e8dd68a3af7","tid":1914390,"uid":350138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb69b99ce92f0b07c10e6b0d821c34c81a7f27be","tid":1914390,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"留名待睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"sor手殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地整嘅簡短版 : <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.