取最大程度上實然自治嘅方法，簡單黎講，即係和勇不分。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為，比起 Gene Sharp ，港人更加需要涉取組織工運嘅知識，以及民眾武力抗爭嘅理據。<br />\n<br />\n按照依嫁嘅發展，中國變天係遲早嘅事，可惜依嫁右翼民粹流行。其實香港體量咁細，根本冇可能憑自力就可以行孤立主義個套。如果要喺自治再走多一步，處理中國民主係無可避免嘅事。"},{"pid":"bc31365d6d056d1e6eb46efaff67899ead6dc6a5","tid":1914390,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T15:56:36.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc77f3469bd7748d5dd5dd7123f1ebc10d06172a","tid":1914390,"uid":21628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T15:59:53.000Z","msg":"啱晒慣咗即食既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef70148cb5e7f317ee79fda9ac8062a7d10e131","tid":1914390,"uid":21628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae92efeac427003f0f131ed2e352080b363836f","tid":1914390,"uid":350138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"184572a0e37cb1b7b8e55a9f1d165989661ec8d9","tid":1914390,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"唔好整簡體流上去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3018335e56ae51c7d4cbcb56c98390429cdd4413","tid":1914390,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6968fb961f767cec634c3c2d988f3c7169341f40","tid":1914390,"uid":272445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"留名待J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\