s://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2F3r1xcmhbm1bzags%2Fhkdemocr.pdf%3Fdl%3D0&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=3dbc0cf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/3r1xcmhbm1bzags/hkdemocr.pdf?dl=0</a>"},{"pid":"f83b6a0a8ef5d0226a9bae443a5b98f1a737d704","tid":1914390,"uid":349661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:35:17.000Z","msg":"G持<br />\n巴打有無諗過開IG account俾多啲人見到？"},{"pid":"2960f641689f9095103448c9a237e02c7ba7b281","tid":1914390,"uid":267622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:01:36.000Z","msg":"有小小噉睇緊<br />\n不如一節一節噉擺出嚟，一齊討論下啦"},{"pid":"5ff7a9bc7158deafc2352ccb58321df26411f719","tid":1914390,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T14:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe14406bc31ceedeaf85163e0d73f4e2c8e838e","tid":1914390,"uid":350138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f83b6a0a8ef5d0226a9bae443a5b98f1a737d704","tid":1914390,"uid":349661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:35:17.000Z","msg":"G持<br />\n巴打有無諗過開IG account俾多啲人見到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T14:18:32.000Z","msg":"謝謝啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地整圖唔叻<br />\n如果有巴絲識整歡迎大家拎去用再廣傳<br />\n<br />\n如果得嘅又有得恆常講唔同書都幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但得我地兩個就好似難啲"}],"pinned":{"pid":"7fb5d2d42206c5b108afb08878b947f72cfe5505","tid":1914390,"uid":350138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:49:49.000Z","msg":"我地都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺序戴左個頭盔<br />\n//我們堅信「兄弟爬山」此座右銘，但亦相信抗爭者可以更有效地運用個人力量，在街頭衝突以外轉戰其他非暴力政治反抗，如抵制和罷工。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">這絕非出於我們不認同目前抗爭者所為</span></strong>，而是事實上，政府於武力運用上不幸地永遠遠超抗爭者。//<br />\n<br />\n前線巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}